Revision history for Sphinx-Manager

0.01    2008-07-26
        First release

0.02	2008-07-29
	Handling of system() return status changed to avoid spurious ECHILD.

0.03	2009-10-21
	Added sudo support.

0.04	2010-04-09
	Added $ok_if_running flag to start_searchd.

0.05	2010-04-09
	Relaxed reload so that error won't be raised if something else starts
	searchd concurrently

0.06    2011-03-23
        Required Sphinx::Config 0.09 due to failing test case.
